POST
/api/v1/auth/login
Login


Authenticate using email and password. Returns a JWT token valid for 24 hours. Send this token in all subsequent requests as: Authorization: Bearer . Works for all roles: CITIZEN, SERVICE_OFFICER, DEPARTMENT_HEAD, CITY_ADMINISTRATOR, COMPLIANCE_OFFICER.

